{"thag4.7:0.1":"Theragatha 4.7 ","thag4.7:0.2":"Catukkanipata ","thag4.7:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag4.7:0.4":"Sambhutattheragatha ","thag4.7:1.1":"“Yo dandhakale tarati, ","thag4.7:1.2":"taraniye ca dandhaye; ","thag4.7:1.3":"Ayoni samvidhanena, ","thag4.7:1.4":"balo dukkham nigacchati. ","thag4.7:2.1":"Tassattha parihayanti, ","thag4.7:2.2":"kalapakkheva candima; ","thag4.7:2.3":"Ayasakyanca pappoti, ","thag4.7:2.4":"mittehi ca virujjhati. ","thag4.7:3.1":"Yo dandhakale dandheti, ","thag4.7:3.2":"taraniye ca taraye; ","thag4.7:3.3":"Yoniso samvidhanena, ","thag4.7:3.4":"sukham pappoti pandito. ","thag4.7:4.1":"Tassattha paripurenti, ","thag4.7:4.2":"sukkapakkheva candima; ","thag4.7:4.3":"Yaso kittinca pappoti, ","thag4.7:4.4":"mittehi na virujjhati”ti. ","thag4.7:4.5":"… Sambhuto thero …. "}